text: Steam Valve, Epic Games, EA Origin, Battle net Blizzard, Microsoft Store, Github, Canva, Twitch tv. Amazon, Alexa, perusahaan nya terdaftar di Direktorat jenderal pajak bukan di PSE. klo Kominfo blokir maka Menteri Keuangan bertindak karena penerimaan pajak berkurang.
en_text: Steam Valve, Epic Games, EA Origin, Battle Net Blizzard, Microsoft Store, Github, Canva, TWitch TV. Amazon, Alexa, the company is registered with the Directorate General of Taxes not at PSE. If the Ministry of Communication and Information is blocked, the Minister of Finance acts because the tax revenue is reduced.
